013package org.apache.juneau.httppart;
014
015/**
016 * Represents possible enum values that can be passed to the {@link HttpPartSerializerSession#serialize(HttpPartType, HttpPartSchema, Object)}.
017 *
018 * <ul class='seealso'>
019 *    <li class='link'><a class="doclink" href="../../../../overview-summary.html#juneau-marshall.jm.HttpPartSerializersParsers">HTTP Part Serializers and Parsers</a>
020 * </ul>
021 */
022public enum HttpPartType {
023
024   /** An HTTP request body */
025   BODY,
026
027   /** A URI path variable */
028   PATH,
029
030   /** A URI query parameter */
031   QUERY,
032
033   /** A form-data parameter */
034   FORMDATA,
035
036   /** An HTTP request header */
037   HEADER,
038
039   /** An HTTP response header */
040   RESPONSE_HEADER,
041
042   /** An HTTP response body */
043   RESPONSE_BODY,
044
045   /** An HTTP response status code */
046   RESPONSE_STATUS,
047
048   /** Generic part */
049   ANY,
050
051   /** A non-standard field */
052   OTHER,
053}
